title: Please Don't Tell Me Who I Am
description: The crew shares their experiences with summer camps and find out about the time Jacob was the only non Hasidic person all Hasidic Jewish camp. The guys discuss the new documentary "Tell Me Who I Am" and how they would feel in the same situation.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
